 \displaystyle \int_{0}^{\pi} \frac{e^{ik{Re^{i \theta}}}}{Re^{i \theta}-a} Re^{i \theta} i \ d \theta = \int_{0}^{\pi} \frac{e^{- k R \sin \theta} \big(\cos (kR \cos \theta)+ i \sin(kR \cos \theta) \big) }{Re^{i \theta} - a} Re^{i \theta} i \ d \theta,
e^{-R\sin\theta}\leq e^{(-2R/\pi)\theta}
\frac{\pi}{2}\leq\theta\leq\pi
